# Technical Stack
Referenced in: [001-project-overview.mdc](001-project-overview.mdc)

## Frontend (React/Vite)
- **Language:** JavaScript (JSX)
- **Framework:** React 18.x
- **Build Tool:** Vite 5.x
- **Styling:** CSS (Inline Styles, index.css)
- **Routing:** React Router DOM
- **State:** React Hooks (useState, useEffect)
- **HTTP Client:** Fetch API (apiClient.js 래퍼)

## Backend (Spring Boot) - 별도 레포지토리
- **Language:** Java 17 (LTS)
- **Framework:** Spring Boot 3.x
- **Build Tool:** Maven 또는 Gradle
- **Database:** 
  - 개발: H2 In-Memory Database
  - 운영: MySQL 8.x
- **ORM:** Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
- **API 문서:** Swagger/OpenAPI 3.0
- **인증:** JWT (JSON Web Token)

## AI Service
- **Provider:** Google Gemini API
- **용도:** GEMS 안전 지능 시스템 (위험 분석)
- **연동:** REST API를 통한 백엔드 게이트웨이

## Infrastructure
- **Frontend 배포:** Vercel
- **Backend 배포:** (TBD)
- **Version Control:** Git + GitHub

